<Layout
  title="Lash Extensions and Eye Health | Safety Guide | Orange County Experts"
  description="Maintaining healthy eyes while wearing lash extensions is easy with proper care. Expert eye health guidance from Orange County lash professionals."
  keywords="lash extension safety, eye health, lash hygiene, Orange County lashes, safe lash extensions"
